1
00:01:37,970 --> 00:01:40,979
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,060 --> 00:01:43,979
[Episode 2]

3
00:01:51,710 --> 00:01:53,039
Who are you looking for?

4
00:01:58,890 --> 00:01:59,590
Sorry.

5
00:01:59,590 --> 00:02:00,760
I got the wrong room.

6
00:02:04,150 --> 00:02:05,000
Yucheng!

7
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:08,300
Was this lady looking for you?

8
00:02:10,310 --> 00:02:11,570
You seem a bit nervous.

9
00:02:19,270 --> 00:02:20,060
Who?

10
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:24,840
Miyu?

11
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:27,500
What are you two doing?

12
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:28,630
Hot gossip

13
00:02:28,630 --> 00:02:29,840
in the early morning.

14
00:02:29,860 --> 00:02:30,920
So you're Mrs. Nie.

15
00:02:31,230 --> 00:02:32,790
Yucheng has told me about you.

16
00:02:32,790 --> 00:02:34,450
Have we met somewhere before?

17
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,570
You go back in. Go.

18
00:02:37,870 --> 00:02:38,630
Don't get it wrong.

19
00:02:38,630 --> 00:02:40,360
This isn't what you think it is.

20
00:02:41,790 --> 00:02:43,280
Why did you push me in?

21
00:02:43,310 --> 00:02:45,120
I didn't finish talking to Mrs. Nie.

22
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,020
Are you out of your mind?

23
00:02:46,020 --> 00:02:47,000
What are you afraid of?

24
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,660
Why are you raising your voice?

25
00:02:48,660 --> 00:02:49,680
Do you want everyone to hear you?

26
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:50,300
So what if they hear me?

27
00:02:50,300 --> 00:02:51,000
What's wrong with that?

28
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:51,560
Can you just go in the room?

29
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:52,400
Nie Yucheng!

30
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:54,140
Did you tell me to come
so I could see this?

31
00:02:54,140 --> 00:02:54,700
No...

32
00:02:56,030 --> 00:02:57,280
Miyu. Miyu!

33
00:02:57,910 --> 00:02:59,040
Where are you going?

34
00:03:00,150 --> 00:03:01,010
Lu Zhenzhen...

35
00:03:02,490 --> 00:03:03,030
Miyu!

36
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:20,540
Miyu!

37
00:03:21,550 --> 00:03:22,390
Miyu!

38
00:03:23,780 --> 00:03:24,930
Miyu!

39
00:03:56,590 --> 00:03:59,110
Low battery. Please replace batteries.

40
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:06,840
These shampoos of yours work quite well.

41
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:08,170
I'm taking them with me.

42
00:04:09,790 --> 00:04:12,580
Look how many pearl necklaces
you've bought.

43
00:04:13,850 --> 00:04:15,020
Do you even

44
00:04:15,040 --> 00:04:16,120
get to wear all of these?

45
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:17,290
Take them if you like.

46
00:04:17,290 --> 00:04:18,950
I'll take them all then, okay?

47
00:04:19,730 --> 00:04:21,459
Why are you looking like this?

48
00:04:22,270 --> 00:04:23,130
Come over here.

49
00:04:23,350 --> 00:04:25,010
Let me see you in better light.

50
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:29,200
Let me see.

51
00:04:32,150 --> 00:04:33,740
Look at yourself.

52
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:35,640
You've got dark circles under your eyes.

53
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:37,440
Fine lines are starting to grow.

54
00:04:37,590 --> 00:04:38,590
Listen up,

55
00:04:38,950 --> 00:04:40,830
you're not a young girl anymore.

56
00:04:40,990 --> 00:04:42,620
It's time you began
taking care of your skin.

57
00:04:42,620 --> 00:04:43,620
Got it?

58
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:46,680
Low battery. Please replace batteries.

59
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,940
Someone's at the door.

60
00:04:48,060 --> 00:04:48,770
Ignore it.

61
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,760
Open up. It's me.

62
00:04:51,909 --> 00:04:52,680
It's Yucheng.

63
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:54,280
-Go open the door!
-I'll do it.

64
00:04:54,280 --> 00:04:55,409
Don't open the door!

65
00:04:56,300 --> 00:04:58,950
-What happened? Did you get into a fight?
-Miyu! Open up, Miyu!

66
00:04:58,950 --> 00:05:02,040
-Whatever it is, sit down and talk to him.
-Don't butt in.

67
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,900
-Just don't open the door.
-Miyu!

68
00:05:05,310 --> 00:05:06,430
It's me. Open the door!

69
00:05:06,430 --> 00:05:07,270
Miyu!

70
00:05:09,270 --> 00:05:10,240
It's high time we left.

71
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,070
We've got things to do.

72
00:05:11,070 --> 00:05:11,830
Hurry up.

73
00:05:12,070 --> 00:05:12,390
Stop eating.

74
00:05:12,390 --> 00:05:13,680
Tidy up the table for your aunt.

75
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:14,940
Hurry. Let me fix this.

76
00:05:19,430 --> 00:05:20,000
Well,

77
00:05:20,510 --> 00:05:21,510
we can't leave

78
00:05:21,510 --> 00:05:23,370
without opening the door, right?

79
00:05:27,270 --> 00:05:28,890
-You're back, Yucheng.
-Zhigang.

80
00:05:28,890 --> 00:05:29,690
Welcome back.

81
00:05:30,430 --> 00:05:31,000
Hand that to me.

82
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,270
Let Zhigang carry it for you.

83
00:05:32,270 --> 00:05:33,270
Just put it there.

84
00:05:33,630 --> 00:05:34,680
My sister never stays mad for long.

85
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:36,010
Just try to cheer her up.

86
00:05:36,520 --> 00:05:37,560
Why not stay for lunch

87
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,680
before you leave?

88
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:39,480
Sounds great.

89
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:42,680
Then we can tell my sister and her husband

90
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:44,270
what happened last night.

91
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,430
A-Alright.

92
00:05:46,450 --> 00:05:48,940
We'd better stay out of your own business.

93
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:52,240
Don't push your luck.

94
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:54,680
Watch your mouth. Don't make things worse.

95
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:57,750
We're getting going.

96
00:05:57,750 --> 00:05:58,480
Okay.

97
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,160
No need to see us out.

98
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:00,680
Really.

99
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:02,160
Let's eat together some other day.

100
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:02,720
Sure.

101
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:04,320
Smooth things over with her.

102
00:06:04,490 --> 00:06:05,560
Take care!

103
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,600
Let me carry this.

104
00:06:25,780 --> 00:06:26,240
Miyu...

105
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:27,100
Don't touch me.

106
00:06:29,010 --> 00:06:30,210
I want a word with you.

107
00:06:30,230 --> 00:06:30,940
About what?

108
00:06:33,370 --> 00:06:34,770
About getting a divorce?

109
00:06:35,159 --> 00:06:35,800
No.

110
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:38,150
You know I'll never walk out on you

111
00:06:38,150 --> 00:06:40,850
-or our home. Please hear me out...
-Then, yesterday,

112
00:06:40,850 --> 00:06:42,450
how did you leave this place?

113
00:06:42,730 --> 00:06:43,360
When you were

114
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:45,360
intimate with another woman in bed,

115
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:47,520
did you think about our home?

116
00:06:48,080 --> 00:06:49,340
Did you think about me?

117
00:06:50,230 --> 00:06:52,380
What happened yesterday
was not as ugly as you think.

118
00:06:52,380 --> 00:06:53,380
It really wasn't.

119
00:06:53,409 --> 00:06:54,480
Something must be wrong with that wine.

120
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:54,920
Listen,

121
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,600
-it must've been spiked. I fell...
-Nie Yucheng!

122
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:58,250
-I fell unconscious after drinking it.
-What story are you making up now?

123
00:06:58,250 --> 00:06:59,040
Will you please hear me out?

124
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:00,420
I'm not making up a story!

125
00:07:00,420 --> 00:07:01,250
Look.

126
00:07:01,090 --> 00:07:03,400
[Lu Zhenzhen, sales rep of Yuhua Hotel]

127
00:07:01,280 --> 00:07:02,360
This is my chat history

128
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,610
with Lu Zhenzhen, alright?

129
00:07:03,610 --> 00:07:04,130
Look.

130
00:07:04,470 --> 00:07:04,920
She kept...

131
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:06,160
-I don't want to watch this!
-She kept sending me messages.

132
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,720
-My replies were plain and simple.
-I don't want to watch this!

133
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:08,830
Will you just take a look?

134
00:07:08,830 --> 00:07:10,510
She knew I was at the hotel,

135
00:07:10,530 --> 00:07:11,360
so she asked to see me

136
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,480
and show me a proposal.

137
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,360
That's all there was to it.

138
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:14,920
Now I feel sick just at the sight of you.

139
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:15,920
I'm sorry. Sorry.

140
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:16,930
I apologize to you.

141
00:07:16,930 --> 00:07:17,930
I did wrong.

142
00:07:17,960 --> 00:07:19,130
I'm regretting it, okay?

143
00:07:19,130 --> 00:07:20,450
Get lost!

144
00:08:10,300 --> 00:08:11,850
[Dad]

145
00:08:13,090 --> 00:08:14,430
Hey, Miyu.

146
00:08:13,250 --> 00:08:15,730
[Microphone On] [Speaker On] [Camera On]

147
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:15,820
What are you doing?

148
00:08:16,010 --> 00:08:16,970
Dad, it's me.

149
00:08:17,020 --> 00:08:19,020
[Microphone On] [Speaker On] [Camera On]

150
00:08:17,990 --> 00:08:19,250
Oh, it's you, Yucheng.

151
00:08:19,300 --> 00:08:20,700
Why is it you on the phone?

152
00:08:22,550 --> 00:08:23,440
Thank you

153
00:08:23,470 --> 00:08:24,800
for buying me a new phone.

154
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:26,260
It's working pretty well.

155
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,240
Don't mention it.

156
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:27,920
We're family.

157
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:29,320
I'm just glad you like it.

158
00:08:31,980 --> 00:08:32,860
Miyu!

159
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,480
I'm on a video call with Dad.

160
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:35,270
Come out now.

161
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,340
Miyu,

162
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:38,840
Dad wants to talk to you.

163
00:08:39,789 --> 00:08:41,030
Why not come out?

164
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,160
Miyu!

165
00:08:45,190 --> 00:08:45,790
Miyu...

166
00:08:45,810 --> 00:08:47,290
What happened to her? Is she okay?

167
00:08:47,290 --> 00:08:48,190
Nothing happened.

168
00:08:48,190 --> 00:08:48,790
She's just tired

169
00:08:48,790 --> 00:08:49,790
and feeling a bit unwell,

170
00:08:49,790 --> 00:08:51,070
so she's lying in bed in our bedroom.

171
00:08:51,070 --> 00:08:52,670
She'll be with us in a moment.

172
00:08:57,790 --> 00:08:59,360
Yes, we had a great time

173
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,910
and took lots of photos.

174
00:09:01,790 --> 00:09:02,390
Dad, seriously,

175
00:09:02,390 --> 00:09:04,240
that hotel is exceptionally beautiful.

176
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:05,890
Let me show you our guesthouse.

177
00:09:05,890 --> 00:09:06,580
Really?

178
00:09:06,690 --> 00:09:07,620
Let me see.

179
00:09:09,650 --> 00:09:10,480
Wait a second.

180
00:09:11,750 --> 00:09:13,480
Dad is showing us the Xu family inn.

181
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,410
Come have a look.

182
00:09:14,920 --> 00:09:16,120
Dad, Miyu is here.

183
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:18,360
Let me show you around.

184
00:09:19,790 --> 00:09:21,030
Look at the entrance.

185
00:09:21,150 --> 00:09:22,480
Impressive, huh?

186
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:25,440
"Xu Family Inn."

187
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:28,360
I specially asked Mr. Cao
to inscribe the sign.

188
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:29,560
This cabinet right at the entrance

189
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:30,750
was picked by Miyu.

190
00:09:31,920 --> 00:09:32,930
Here's a bonsai.

191
00:09:32,970 --> 00:09:34,520
Look at these decorations.

192
00:09:34,630 --> 00:09:35,760
Incredible, right?

193
00:09:36,930 --> 00:09:38,340
Listen,

194
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:41,030
Miyu's interest in art has really

195
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:42,270
come in handy.

196
00:09:42,700 --> 00:09:45,000
It's truly useful at critical moments.

197
00:09:45,030 --> 00:09:45,790
Right?

198
00:09:47,030 --> 00:09:47,630
By the way,

199
00:09:47,740 --> 00:09:48,460
well, we...

200
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:50,650
genuinely hope you can refer as many

201
00:09:51,030 --> 00:09:52,970
tour groups as possible to our inn.

202
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:55,690
The furnishings of this place

203
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:57,150
are definitely the best

204
00:09:57,170 --> 00:09:58,840
for miles around.

205
00:09:58,870 --> 00:09:59,480
Rest assured.

206
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:01,110
Visitors won't be disappointed
when they arrive.

207
00:10:01,110 --> 00:10:03,500
I don't need to conduct a quality check
before referring clients to you.

208
00:10:03,500 --> 00:10:04,500
We're family.

209
00:10:04,530 --> 00:10:06,190
Who else would I refer clients to,
if not you?

210
00:10:06,190 --> 00:10:06,980
That's right.

211
00:10:06,980 --> 00:10:07,780
We're family.

212
00:10:19,750 --> 00:10:21,000
Dad, how about this?

213
00:10:21,020 --> 00:10:23,230
I'll take a day of annual leave
in a few days

214
00:10:23,230 --> 00:10:24,510
and visit the family inn with Miyu,

215
00:10:24,510 --> 00:10:25,120
okay?

216
00:10:25,390 --> 00:10:26,320
Sure.

217
00:10:26,470 --> 00:10:27,390
I'll cook something nice

218
00:10:27,390 --> 00:10:29,030
for you when you're here.

219
00:10:29,270 --> 00:10:30,630
Yucheng, you love

220
00:10:30,630 --> 00:10:32,280
the ornamental pastries I make,

221
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:33,070
don't you?

222
00:10:33,370 --> 00:10:35,530
My mouth is watering upon hearing it.

223
00:10:35,630 --> 00:10:38,030
Shall we pay a visit this weekend?

224
00:10:39,610 --> 00:10:40,740
Get your hand off me.

225
00:10:42,550 --> 00:10:43,300
Miyu,

226
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:44,510
Yucheng's talking to you nicely.

227
00:10:44,510 --> 00:10:45,270
Why do you have to take

228
00:10:45,270 --> 00:10:46,600
this attitude with him?

229
00:10:46,880 --> 00:10:49,080
Don't throw temper tantrums, alright?

230
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:50,480
Mom, Dad,

231
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:51,480
you're mistaken.

232
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,960
We just got back from abroad.

233
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:53,720
Miyu was unpacking

234
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:54,550
and probably got tired.

235
00:10:54,550 --> 00:10:55,680
Everything's fine.

236
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:56,600
You guys talk.

237
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:57,720
I'll go cook.

238
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:34,080
Yucheng, well...

239
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:36,530
If there's a problem, talk it through.

240
00:11:36,640 --> 00:11:37,840
I know best about

241
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:39,360
my daughter's temper.

242
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:40,840
Her anger never lasts long.

243
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:41,720
A few days, at most.

244
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:42,840
Okay. I'll talk to her.

245
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:43,720
Don't worry.

246
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:45,240
Every problem can be solved.

247
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:46,690
I have faith in Yucheng.

248
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:48,410
You're a brilliant young man.

249
00:11:48,410 --> 00:11:50,960
Alright. Go back to what you were doing.

250
00:11:51,020 --> 00:11:52,420
We'd hate to disturb you.

251
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:53,610
Take care, Mom, Dad.

252
00:11:53,660 --> 00:11:54,320
I'm hanging up now.

253
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:55,320
-Bye.
-Okay, bye.

254
00:12:02,860 --> 00:12:03,610
[Dad]

255
00:12:03,670 --> 00:12:04,530
[WeChat]

256
00:12:06,290 --> 00:12:07,120
[Honey]

257
00:12:07,180 --> 00:12:07,810
[WeChat]

258
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:08,540
[Babe, send the blue shirt I usually wear]

259
00:12:08,570 --> 00:12:09,290
[to Room 1819, Purong Hotel,
at 6:00 tomorrow]

260
00:12:09,310 --> 00:12:10,030
[No need to reply. Love you]

261
00:12:15,380 --> 00:12:17,390
[Honey]

262
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:19,330
[Babe, send the blue shirt I usually wear]

263
00:12:19,350 --> 00:12:19,890
[to Room 1819, Purong Hotel,
at 6:00 tomorrow]

264
00:12:25,920 --> 00:12:26,400
Mom.

265
00:12:26,530 --> 00:12:27,260
Yucheng,

266
00:12:27,450 --> 00:12:30,260
I'd like to speak to Miyu.

267
00:12:30,820 --> 00:12:31,720
Sure. Just a moment.

268
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:33,180
I'll pass the phone to her.

269
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:40,320
What's wrong with me?

270
00:12:42,700 --> 00:12:43,540
Miyu.

271
00:12:45,180 --> 00:12:46,580
Mom wants to speak to you.

272
00:12:50,990 --> 00:12:51,650
Mom.

273
00:12:51,730 --> 00:12:52,540
Miyu,

274
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:55,920
your sister told me everything
when she came back.

275
00:12:55,920 --> 00:12:58,120
I know you got into a fight with Yucheng.

276
00:12:58,480 --> 00:12:59,670
I already noticed that

277
00:12:59,670 --> 00:13:01,200
on the previous video call.

278
00:13:01,510 --> 00:13:02,670
When you're mad,

279
00:13:02,920 --> 00:13:05,360
sulk or throw a tantrum as you like.

280
00:13:06,120 --> 00:13:06,840
However,

281
00:13:07,010 --> 00:13:08,610
don't get out of line.

282
00:13:08,900 --> 00:13:09,690
Mom,

283
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:11,120
you have no idea.

284
00:13:11,870 --> 00:13:12,390
Nie Yucheng actually...

285
00:13:12,390 --> 00:13:13,250
I know.

286
00:13:13,280 --> 00:13:14,760
I know how you must feel.

287
00:13:15,440 --> 00:13:16,790
He has upset you.

288
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:19,090
But you must be clear about one thing.

289
00:13:19,090 --> 00:13:21,810
That is, your husband
is providing for you now.

290
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:23,720
No matter what has happened,

291
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:24,480
just sit down,

292
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:26,950
talk it through,
and the problem will go away.

293
00:13:26,950 --> 00:13:28,000
I saw how Nie Yucheng

294
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:30,250
treated you just now.

295
00:13:30,280 --> 00:13:31,950
He was talking sweet to you, wasn't he?

296
00:13:31,950 --> 00:13:34,070
If he intended to leave you,

297
00:13:34,090 --> 00:13:35,240
he would just ignore you

298
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:37,210
no matter how you tried to sweet talk him.

299
00:13:37,210 --> 00:13:38,820
How could you say that, Mom?

300
00:13:38,970 --> 00:13:40,370
My words may sound harsh,

301
00:13:40,630 --> 00:13:42,820
but they're all for your own good.

302
00:13:42,950 --> 00:13:44,190
Think about it.

303
00:13:44,210 --> 00:13:46,860
Given Yucheng's current wealth
and social status,

304
00:13:46,860 --> 00:13:49,740
plus his car and house in Shanghai,

305
00:13:50,210 --> 00:13:51,840
a great number of temptresses

306
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:53,480
are eager to take your place.

307
00:13:54,030 --> 00:13:55,540
What will become of you

308
00:13:55,560 --> 00:13:56,800
if you fall out with him?

309
00:13:56,800 --> 00:13:58,660
Have you ever thought about that?

310
00:13:58,660 --> 00:14:00,190
I've been where you are now.

311
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:02,600
Having someone to rely on

312
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:05,120
is better than suffering alone out there.

313
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:06,840
Don't act silly.

314
00:14:06,870 --> 00:14:08,800
Don't give away your lovely home

315
00:14:08,820 --> 00:14:10,340
to someone else.

316
00:14:10,960 --> 00:14:13,270
Besides, get pregnant soon.

317
00:14:14,190 --> 00:14:15,280
Do you hear me?

318
00:14:21,500 --> 00:14:22,380
Yes.

319
00:14:54,990 --> 00:14:55,350
[Jane]

320
00:14:56,420 --> 00:14:58,490
[Photos and videos]

321
00:15:02,100 --> 00:15:04,100
Lu Zhenzhen, you tricked me?

322
00:15:21,870 --> 00:15:22,610
[Jane]

323
00:15:25,020 --> 00:15:26,960
You'd better give me a good reason.

324
00:15:42,360 --> 00:15:43,440
I'm pregnant.

325
00:16:23,250 --> 00:16:23,890
Miyu?

326
00:17:44,720 --> 00:17:45,890
I heated some milk for you.

327
00:17:45,890 --> 00:17:47,010
Drink it when you get up.

328
00:17:47,010 --> 00:17:47,940
Love you, Honey.

329
00:17:54,990 --> 00:17:58,600
[Changyang Travel]

330
00:17:56,030 --> 00:17:57,830
I heard that this business trip

331
00:17:57,930 --> 00:17:58,680
happened to

332
00:17:58,680 --> 00:18:00,830
coincide with
your 10th wedding anniversary.

333
00:18:00,830 --> 00:18:02,480
Your wife traveled all the way abroad

334
00:18:02,480 --> 00:18:03,830
to surprise you, didn't she?

335
00:18:03,830 --> 00:18:04,560
Yes, she did.

336
00:18:05,070 --> 00:18:06,480
We had no choice.

337
00:18:06,590 --> 00:18:08,400
After all,
the luxury wilderness overseas tours

338
00:18:08,400 --> 00:18:09,510
are the company's most important

339
00:18:09,510 --> 00:18:11,200
strategic plan for the next few years.

340
00:18:11,200 --> 00:18:12,050
In fact, Miyu

341
00:18:12,110 --> 00:18:13,770
is very supportive of my work.

342
00:18:14,350 --> 00:18:15,310
You truly married

343
00:18:15,310 --> 00:18:16,590
the right woman,

344
00:18:16,830 --> 00:18:17,750
for she brings you good fortune.

345
00:18:17,750 --> 00:18:19,030
You must cherish her.

346
00:18:19,030 --> 00:18:19,720
I know.

347
00:18:19,720 --> 00:18:20,520
I surely will.

348
00:18:21,030 --> 00:18:23,030
Any updates on the Svelto Hotel Group?

349
00:18:23,030 --> 00:18:24,550
Everything's going smoothly.

350
00:18:24,550 --> 00:18:25,960
Since the hotel's general manager there

351
00:18:25,960 --> 00:18:26,890
is also Chinese,

352
00:18:27,110 --> 00:18:29,720
there's no cultural barrier
in communication at all.

353
00:18:29,720 --> 00:18:31,690
We'll set up a group and connect online
next week

354
00:18:31,690 --> 00:18:32,720
for a formal meeting.

355
00:18:32,720 --> 00:18:33,510
This overseas project

356
00:18:33,510 --> 00:18:34,640
is a long-term endeavor.

357
00:18:34,640 --> 00:18:36,240
I believe in your abilities.

358
00:18:36,350 --> 00:18:39,000
But, as for the Yufeng Jiangnan project,

359
00:18:39,000 --> 00:18:40,660
I hope you'll give it your all.

360
00:18:41,350 --> 00:18:42,810
Just between you and me,

361
00:18:42,870 --> 00:18:44,530
the position of vice president

362
00:18:44,530 --> 00:18:46,640
will either be yours or Yin's.

363
00:18:47,030 --> 00:18:48,960
The others are no match for you.

364
00:18:49,550 --> 00:18:50,920
You know who's backing Yin

365
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:52,310
without me saying, right?

366
00:18:52,310 --> 00:18:53,030
Yes, I do.

367
00:18:53,030 --> 00:18:55,960
You'll have more leverage
as long as you nail

368
00:18:55,960 --> 00:18:58,510
the Yufeng Jiangnan project.

369
00:18:58,530 --> 00:19:00,850
By then, however powerful
his connections are,

370
00:19:00,850 --> 00:19:01,920
he can't beat you.

371
00:19:04,550 --> 00:19:05,960
Thanks for the advice, Mr. Hu.

372
00:19:05,960 --> 00:19:07,490
I'll definitely do my best.

373
00:19:10,790 --> 00:19:14,760
[Yuhua Hotel]

374
00:19:23,770 --> 00:19:24,650
Hello, ma'am.

375
00:19:26,180 --> 00:19:26,640
Hello.

376
00:19:26,640 --> 00:19:28,260
I'm here to meet Lu Zhenzhen
from the sales department.

377
00:19:28,260 --> 00:19:29,790
Okay. Please wait a moment.

378
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:34,110
A lady at the reception

379
00:19:34,110 --> 00:19:36,340
is asking to meet Lu Zhenzhen from sales.

380
00:19:36,340 --> 00:19:38,020
How may I address you, ma'am?

381
00:19:40,590 --> 00:19:41,480
Lu Zhenzhen, listen,

382
00:19:41,480 --> 00:19:42,480
my surname is Xu.

383
00:19:42,750 --> 00:19:44,390
I'll be waiting for you
at the coffee spot across the street.

384
00:19:44,390 --> 00:19:45,880
Meet me there in 30 minutes,

385
00:19:45,880 --> 00:19:48,010
or you'll bear serious consequences.

386
00:20:30,950 --> 00:20:31,880
Why are you so late?

387
00:20:31,880 --> 00:20:32,960
The traffic was terrible today.

388
00:20:32,960 --> 00:20:34,480
That's why I'm late.

389
00:20:45,760 --> 00:20:46,720
What's going on?

390
00:20:48,890 --> 00:20:51,150
Why hasn't the payment been settled yet?

391
00:20:51,810 --> 00:20:53,940
How am I supposed to pay the suppliers?

392
00:20:54,670 --> 00:20:55,910
Rush them, okay?

393
00:20:57,480 --> 00:20:58,240
Talking to Mr. Nie

394
00:20:58,240 --> 00:20:59,770
or Feng Bin won't be of help.

395
00:20:59,830 --> 00:21:00,660
That's it.

396
00:21:06,980 --> 00:21:09,490
Sorry to keep you waiting.

397
00:21:16,730 --> 00:21:17,860
What a coincidence.

398
00:21:17,950 --> 00:21:19,750
Our purses are exactly the same.

399
00:21:21,130 --> 00:21:23,460
I'm not here to talk about purses
with you.

400
00:21:24,590 --> 00:21:26,250
That was just an opening line.

401
00:21:26,430 --> 00:21:28,370
Why create so much tension?

402
00:21:28,800 --> 00:21:29,880
I was going to compliment you

403
00:21:29,880 --> 00:21:31,350
on your taste, Mrs. Nie.

404
00:21:32,130 --> 00:21:33,910
Leather and jewelry.

405
00:21:34,590 --> 00:21:36,590
Wild and elegant.

406
00:21:37,830 --> 00:21:39,370
But this combination doesn't

407
00:21:39,370 --> 00:21:41,030
really pair with your outfit.

408
00:21:41,500 --> 00:21:42,900
A bit too rigid, isn't it?

409
00:21:43,230 --> 00:21:45,890
These opening lines of yours
are not quite good.

410
00:21:46,840 --> 00:21:48,170
Who bought you this bag?

411
00:21:49,390 --> 00:21:50,870
Can't I buy it myself?

412
00:21:55,590 --> 00:21:56,350
Waitress.

413
00:21:56,740 --> 00:21:57,940
We're ready to order.

414
00:22:01,760 --> 00:22:02,640
I'll have a...

415
00:22:02,640 --> 00:22:04,440
I'll have a lemonade, thank you.

416
00:22:08,070 --> 00:22:08,870
I'll go with this one.

417
00:22:08,870 --> 00:22:10,500
Fantasy of the Deep Forest.

418
00:22:10,520 --> 00:22:11,520
Okay, ma'am.

419
00:22:17,510 --> 00:22:19,970
[Yuhua Hotel Frequent Guest Program]

420
00:22:30,640 --> 00:22:31,350
Go ahead.

421
00:22:31,830 --> 00:22:33,230
Why did you want to see me?

422
00:22:33,750 --> 00:22:35,120
Didn't you ask to see me?

423
00:22:45,640 --> 00:22:48,570
You sent me Wechat messages
from my husband's phone.

424
00:22:48,640 --> 00:22:50,970
Wasn't that just an excuse
to get to see me?

425
00:22:52,270 --> 00:22:53,790
Mrs. Nie, I think you may have

426
00:22:53,790 --> 00:22:54,880
misunderstood those messages.

427
00:22:54,880 --> 00:22:56,070
Then what's the truth?

428
00:22:56,070 --> 00:22:57,310
Didn't your husband tell you?

429
00:22:57,310 --> 00:22:58,750
What my husband tells me

430
00:22:58,750 --> 00:23:00,400
is between the two of us.

431
00:23:00,680 --> 00:23:02,680
I want to hear your side of the story.

432
00:23:02,960 --> 00:23:04,690
How did you two know each other?

433
00:23:04,750 --> 00:23:05,750
You mean Mr. Nie?

434
00:23:06,440 --> 00:23:08,110
We met through work. That's all.

435
00:23:08,110 --> 00:23:09,920
What kind of work is so complicated

436
00:23:09,920 --> 00:23:12,380
that it needs to be settled
in his hotel room?

437
00:23:12,510 --> 00:23:13,680
Mrs. Nie.

438
00:23:13,840 --> 00:23:15,600
I'm just an employee.

439
00:23:15,840 --> 00:23:17,640
If a client picks the place,

440
00:23:18,040 --> 00:23:19,210
I show up. Simple as that.

441
00:23:19,210 --> 00:23:20,540
So you're saying...

442
00:23:21,310 --> 00:23:23,030
Nie Yucheng was the one
who approached you first?

443
00:23:23,030 --> 00:23:24,200
I never said that.

444
00:23:24,920 --> 00:23:26,180
Mrs. Nie, please don't

445
00:23:26,980 --> 00:23:28,040
get the wrong idea.

446
00:23:28,500 --> 00:23:29,640
I don't want to cause

447
00:23:29,640 --> 00:23:31,710
any misunderstandings
between you and yoru husband.

448
00:23:31,710 --> 00:23:34,970
The last thing I need is to look like
I'm stirring things up.

449
00:23:35,840 --> 00:23:37,630
Sorry, I need to take this call.

450
00:23:41,440 --> 00:23:42,350
Hello, Mr. Yang.

451
00:23:42,350 --> 00:23:43,350
This is Zhenzhen.

452
00:23:43,470 --> 00:23:44,270
What's wrong?

453
00:23:45,270 --> 00:23:47,470
The payment still hasn't gone through?

454
00:23:50,200 --> 00:23:52,330
I'll go see Mr. Nie in person tomorrow.

455
00:23:53,110 --> 00:23:54,110
Don't worry.

456
00:23:54,110 --> 00:23:56,520
I'll get that money back,
even if I have to fight for it.

457
00:23:56,520 --> 00:23:57,680
I'm with a client right now.

458
00:23:57,680 --> 00:23:59,280
Can we talk about this later?

459
00:24:07,020 --> 00:24:07,740
Mrs. Nie.

460
00:24:08,670 --> 00:24:10,270
I came here today

461
00:24:10,400 --> 00:24:11,770
not because I'm afraid of you.

462
00:24:11,770 --> 00:24:13,130
I just want to remind you

463
00:24:13,240 --> 00:24:15,040
to mind your social boundaries.

464
00:24:15,200 --> 00:24:16,750
If a man makes a mistake,

465
00:24:16,750 --> 00:24:18,510
you should settle scores with him.

466
00:24:18,510 --> 00:24:20,000
Don't you think going after the woman

467
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:21,370
is a bit low?

468
00:24:21,480 --> 00:24:23,340
Don't try to bluff your way out.

469
00:24:23,560 --> 00:24:25,690
I called you here to remind you as well.

470
00:24:25,700 --> 00:24:27,200
When you're dealing
with someone else's husband,

471
00:24:27,200 --> 00:24:28,960
you should also
mind your social boundaries.

472
00:24:28,960 --> 00:24:31,420
Being competitive at work
is your strength.

473
00:24:31,940 --> 00:24:33,200
But in relationships,

474
00:24:33,510 --> 00:24:35,200
snatching whatever you see

475
00:24:35,840 --> 00:24:37,480
is nothing but shameless.

476
00:24:40,780 --> 00:24:42,780
Are you saying I stole your husband?

477
00:24:42,840 --> 00:24:44,720
Then let me ask you, Mrs. Nie.

478
00:24:44,840 --> 00:24:46,400
If a man doesn't love me,

479
00:24:47,120 --> 00:24:48,880
why would I even bother?

480
00:24:49,710 --> 00:24:52,560
It takes two to tango.

481
00:24:53,240 --> 00:24:54,720
A man changing his mind

482
00:24:54,750 --> 00:24:56,750
is as common as upgrading a phone.

483
00:24:57,000 --> 00:24:58,560
That's just how it is.

484
00:24:59,550 --> 00:25:00,680
But I suppose

485
00:25:00,680 --> 00:25:02,340
that's a little unfair to you.

486
00:25:03,070 --> 00:25:04,130
You have no income,

487
00:25:04,570 --> 00:25:05,960
no status in the family,

488
00:25:05,990 --> 00:25:07,790
and no social circle of your own.

489
00:25:07,810 --> 00:25:08,970
If it came to divorce,

490
00:25:08,970 --> 00:25:11,120
you'd be the one at a disadvantage.

491
00:25:17,280 --> 00:25:18,480
Since this is our first meeting,

492
00:25:18,480 --> 00:25:20,410
and you've been so upfront with me,

493
00:25:20,530 --> 00:25:22,340
I'll give you some advice too.

494
00:25:22,840 --> 00:25:24,170
I don't have a job,

495
00:25:24,960 --> 00:25:27,350
so maybe I don't get
how things work in your world.

496
00:25:27,350 --> 00:25:28,240
However,

497
00:25:29,240 --> 00:25:31,350
I've been married
to Nie Yucheng for 10 years.

498
00:25:31,350 --> 00:25:32,240
I know him.

499
00:25:32,710 --> 00:25:34,070
Based on what you know about him—

500
00:25:34,070 --> 00:25:35,180
tell me,

501
00:25:35,210 --> 00:25:37,310
if he had to choose

502
00:25:37,310 --> 00:25:39,070
between you and his reputation,

503
00:25:39,070 --> 00:25:40,670
which do you think he'd pick?

504
00:25:41,880 --> 00:25:43,170
What do you mean?

505
00:25:43,750 --> 00:25:45,610
You set me up to catch him cheating

506
00:25:45,670 --> 00:25:48,350
just because you're desperate
to replace me, right?

507
00:25:48,350 --> 00:25:50,740
You couldn't make any progress
with Nie Yucheng,

508
00:25:50,740 --> 00:25:52,800
so now you're coming after me, right?

509
00:25:53,980 --> 00:25:55,380
I've got nothing to lose.

510
00:25:56,030 --> 00:25:56,890
What about you?

511
00:25:57,070 --> 00:25:58,600
You know better than anyone

512
00:25:58,880 --> 00:26:00,210
how easily men

513
00:26:00,310 --> 00:26:01,950
change their minds.

514
00:26:02,310 --> 00:26:04,640
So what makes you think he'd ruin himself,

515
00:26:04,750 --> 00:26:07,010
and bear the cheater label, just for you?

516
00:26:07,240 --> 00:26:09,000
I've heard plenty of

517
00:26:09,000 --> 00:26:10,590
harsh truths in my life.

518
00:26:11,550 --> 00:26:13,010
I only believe in one rule:

519
00:26:13,910 --> 00:26:15,310
survival of the fittest.

520
00:26:16,420 --> 00:26:17,630
It's that simple.

521
00:26:25,670 --> 00:26:27,270
Then I hope you keep winning.

522
00:26:28,850 --> 00:26:30,860
And if you ever lose,

523
00:26:31,120 --> 00:26:33,320
I hope you remember what you said today.

524
00:26:34,170 --> 00:26:35,430
I'll be waiting to see.

525
00:26:52,810 --> 00:26:55,020
[Nie Yucheng]

526
00:26:53,350 --> 00:26:54,880
Has the cat got your tongue?

527
00:27:12,230 --> 00:27:14,880
I called Lu Zhenzhen's bluffing,

528
00:27:14,910 --> 00:27:16,870
but wasn't I doing the same?

529
00:27:17,840 --> 00:27:19,470
Winning an argument

530
00:27:20,070 --> 00:27:22,530
doesn't change the fact
that I was betrayed.

531
00:27:23,950 --> 00:27:25,510
In this war,

532
00:27:26,830 --> 00:27:28,150
there are no winners.

533
00:27:57,880 --> 00:27:58,880
Don't come in yet.

534
00:28:00,430 --> 00:28:01,630
It's a mess in here.

535
00:28:01,950 --> 00:28:03,240
Watch your feet.

536
00:28:03,810 --> 00:28:05,220
I was trying to cook something for you,

537
00:28:05,220 --> 00:28:07,180
but I messed it up.

538
00:28:24,260 --> 00:28:24,720
Hello?

539
00:28:25,310 --> 00:28:26,770
The time can't be changed.

540
00:28:27,030 --> 00:28:28,550
This is their last chance.

541
00:28:28,880 --> 00:28:30,340
We have to hold our ground.

542
00:28:30,960 --> 00:28:32,270
I'll talk to Mr. Wang.

543
00:28:35,060 --> 00:28:36,990
Don't bring up Yuhua again. Got it?

544
00:28:38,270 --> 00:28:39,030
Okay, got it.

545
00:28:39,670 --> 00:28:41,130
I'm with my wife right now.

546
00:28:42,240 --> 00:28:43,180
How about this—

547
00:28:43,550 --> 00:28:45,790
get the project team together later.

548
00:28:45,790 --> 00:28:47,000
Let's do a quick meeting.

549
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:48,400
Alright. I'm hanging up.

550
00:28:55,070 --> 00:28:56,310
Why are you home?

551
00:28:57,640 --> 00:28:59,390
Where else would I go?

552
00:28:59,510 --> 00:29:00,510
This is my home—

553
00:29:01,160 --> 00:29:02,190
our home.

554
00:29:03,070 --> 00:29:06,400
Don't you want me to come home early,
spending time with you?

555
00:29:13,060 --> 00:29:14,450
Don't bother cooking.

556
00:29:14,510 --> 00:29:16,720
We can order in or go out.

557
00:29:18,580 --> 00:29:19,840
Let's just eat at home.

558
00:29:20,390 --> 00:29:21,520
It'll be ready soon.

559
00:29:43,830 --> 00:29:46,070
Aren't you going to ask
where I went today?

560
00:29:46,070 --> 00:29:47,330
Where did you go today?

561
00:29:47,640 --> 00:29:49,040
I went to see Lu Zhenzhen.

562
00:29:57,590 --> 00:29:59,270
That woman is a compulsive liar.

563
00:29:59,270 --> 00:30:00,190
Why did you go see her?

564
00:30:00,190 --> 00:30:01,650
I'm not so sure about that.

565
00:30:02,000 --> 00:30:02,590
At least I know

566
00:30:02,590 --> 00:30:03,590
her limited edition

567
00:30:03,590 --> 00:30:05,440
designer bag is real.

568
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:07,570
That was a gift from our company.

569
00:30:07,570 --> 00:30:09,500
I only suggested the brand.

570
00:30:09,720 --> 00:30:10,990
Who bought you this bag?

571
00:30:10,990 --> 00:30:12,270
Can't I buy it myself?

572
00:30:13,200 --> 00:30:14,200
My relationship with her

573
00:30:14,200 --> 00:30:15,310
isn't what you think.

574
00:30:15,310 --> 00:30:16,030
Really?

575
00:30:16,510 --> 00:30:18,000
So I'm the one with the dirty mind?

576
00:30:18,000 --> 00:30:19,270
What do you mean by that?

577
00:30:19,270 --> 00:30:20,510
I mean,

578
00:30:20,790 --> 00:30:23,520
people like you who have
a spark in the workplace—

579
00:30:23,790 --> 00:30:24,990
you're not cheaters.

580
00:30:25,310 --> 00:30:26,710
You're partners in arms,

581
00:30:27,160 --> 00:30:27,820
right?

582
00:30:31,480 --> 00:30:32,510
Maybe I've been

583
00:30:32,510 --> 00:30:33,970
stuck at home for too long,

584
00:30:34,350 --> 00:30:36,280
I've watched too many soap operas.

585
00:30:36,540 --> 00:30:38,200
When my husband cheated on me,

586
00:30:38,750 --> 00:30:40,920
I assumed it must be
some cheap floozy

587
00:30:40,920 --> 00:30:43,000
who seduced him with her beauty.

588
00:30:44,930 --> 00:30:46,210
How shallow of me.

589
00:30:48,750 --> 00:30:49,960
I can't even imagine

590
00:30:49,960 --> 00:30:51,970
how the two of you work together,

591
00:30:52,350 --> 00:30:53,810
or how deep that bond goes.

592
00:30:54,200 --> 00:30:56,310
All that unspoken tension,

593
00:30:56,510 --> 00:30:57,570
all that friction—

594
00:30:57,910 --> 00:30:59,900
they're way beyond my imagination.

595
00:30:59,900 --> 00:31:01,700
Because I've never had a career.

596
00:31:02,600 --> 00:31:04,810
Career women aren't anything special.

597
00:31:04,940 --> 00:31:06,660
It's just a job.

598
00:31:07,380 --> 00:31:09,030
Think about yourself back then.

599
00:31:09,030 --> 00:31:09,790
You gave up

600
00:31:10,220 --> 00:31:11,430
your career for me,

601
00:31:11,450 --> 00:31:12,640
and chose our family instead.

602
00:31:12,640 --> 00:31:14,750
That's what it means
to fight side by side,

603
00:31:14,750 --> 00:31:16,310
and share the same fate.

604
00:31:16,920 --> 00:31:18,270
Miyu, remember this—

605
00:31:18,640 --> 00:31:19,870
you are my wife.

606
00:31:20,510 --> 00:31:21,840
That will never change.

607
00:31:22,550 --> 00:31:23,070
Never?

608
00:31:23,090 --> 00:31:25,290
At least that's how I feel.

609
00:31:30,900 --> 00:31:32,830
Then whose red underwear was that?

610
00:31:33,310 --> 00:31:34,200
Was it hers?

611
00:31:36,560 --> 00:31:37,430
Was it?

612
00:31:41,790 --> 00:31:42,790
Some things

613
00:31:43,030 --> 00:31:44,430
are better left unknown.

614
00:31:46,510 --> 00:31:47,510
So it was hers.

615
00:31:55,970 --> 00:31:56,900
Fine. I admit it.

616
00:31:57,210 --> 00:31:58,610
She did come to see me.

617
00:31:58,630 --> 00:31:59,900
But I kicked her out.

618
00:31:59,960 --> 00:32:00,510
I never thought

619
00:32:00,510 --> 00:32:02,440
she'd pull a dirty trick like that.

620
00:32:02,590 --> 00:32:03,240
I never thought...

621
00:32:03,240 --> 00:32:05,500
So before I got to the Svelto Hotel Group—

622
00:32:05,550 --> 00:32:07,270
where was she those days?

623
00:32:07,270 --> 00:32:09,430
Was she with you the whole time?

624
00:32:09,480 --> 00:32:11,270
Sure, let me check the room availability.

625
00:32:11,270 --> 00:32:11,920
Okay.

626
00:32:15,270 --> 00:32:16,540
Is there a problem?

627
00:32:16,580 --> 00:32:17,940
Did you change rooms?

628
00:32:19,620 --> 00:32:20,250
Mrs. Nie.

629
00:32:20,680 --> 00:32:22,590
Mr. Nie is a VIP guest at our hotel.

630
00:32:22,590 --> 00:32:24,350
We just upgraded his room

631
00:32:24,370 --> 00:32:25,400
to a suite this morning.

632
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:26,880
But we've already

633
00:32:26,880 --> 00:32:27,570
looked into this thoroughly.

634
00:32:27,570 --> 00:32:28,690
This is entirely

635
00:32:28,720 --> 00:32:30,350
our hotel's responsibility.

636
00:32:30,350 --> 00:32:31,240
So, Mrs. Nie,

637
00:32:31,240 --> 00:32:32,440
please rest assured.

638
00:32:41,790 --> 00:32:42,510
Miyu.

639
00:32:43,030 --> 00:32:45,030
I admit she came to see me those days.

640
00:32:45,070 --> 00:32:46,570
But I swear to you,

641
00:32:46,790 --> 00:32:48,750
we did nothing but work.

642
00:32:48,790 --> 00:32:50,200
Nothing happened.

643
00:32:50,200 --> 00:32:50,930
Understand?

644
00:32:51,420 --> 00:32:52,830
That must've been so hard for you.

645
00:32:52,830 --> 00:32:54,490
Working yourself to the bone,

646
00:32:54,510 --> 00:32:56,270
and still colluding
with the Svelto Hotel Group's

647
00:32:56,270 --> 00:32:57,270
general manager

648
00:32:57,890 --> 00:32:58,920
to lie to me

649
00:32:59,420 --> 00:33:00,820
and cover up your affair.

650
00:33:01,390 --> 00:33:03,320
Birds of a feather flock together.

651
00:33:04,810 --> 00:33:05,570
Miyu.

652
00:33:05,940 --> 00:33:07,740
I didn't mean to hide it from you.

653
00:33:08,660 --> 00:33:10,320
I just didn't want to hurt you.

654
00:33:10,510 --> 00:33:11,790
Lu Zhenzhen is

655
00:33:11,790 --> 00:33:14,000
trying to destroy our family deliberately.

656
00:33:14,000 --> 00:33:15,070
I was scared you'd fall for her tricks.

657
00:33:15,070 --> 00:33:16,130
Do you understand?

658
00:33:21,510 --> 00:33:23,110
You don't believe me, do you?

659
00:33:24,450 --> 00:33:28,050
[Lu Zhenzhen, Yuhua Hotel's Sales Rep]

660
00:33:24,880 --> 00:33:25,750
Lu Zhenzhen—

661
00:33:26,550 --> 00:33:28,080
I'm deleting her right now.

662
00:33:28,510 --> 00:33:30,720
She's out of our lives. For good.

663
00:33:31,510 --> 00:33:33,510
If she ever contacts me again,

664
00:33:33,770 --> 00:33:34,970
I'll talk to her supervisor

665
00:33:34,970 --> 00:33:35,970
and get her fired.

666
00:33:36,610 --> 00:33:38,050
[Friend Settings]

667
00:33:38,130 --> 00:33:39,470
[Delete Contact] [Delete]

668
00:33:39,270 --> 00:33:40,000
Deleted.

669
00:33:39,550 --> 00:33:40,480
[Please wait a moment]

670
00:33:40,540 --> 00:33:40,720
[Friend Settings]

671
00:33:41,280 --> 00:33:42,000
Miyu.

672
00:33:42,880 --> 00:33:44,710
Listen to me. Listen to me.

673
00:33:44,960 --> 00:33:46,720
I won't let anyone hurt you.

674
00:33:47,420 --> 00:33:50,030
You have to believe me on this.

675
00:33:57,760 --> 00:33:58,750
Ms. Lu,

676
00:33:58,790 --> 00:34:00,380
don't put me in a tough spot, okay?

677
00:34:00,380 --> 00:34:02,030
Really, if there's anything, just tell me.

678
00:34:02,030 --> 00:34:04,510
-How many times have I told you? Did it work?
-Let me help you.

679
00:34:04,510 --> 00:34:07,510
-Ms. Lu, Mr. Nie is…
-Don't mind me, just do your thing.

680
00:34:13,100 --> 00:34:14,750
[Yuhua Hotel Co., Ltd.
Statement of Account]

681
00:34:17,920 --> 00:34:19,000
Go find Feng Bin.

682
00:34:19,550 --> 00:34:20,810
He's in charge of this.

683
00:34:21,440 --> 00:34:23,810
Feng Bin has been stalling us
for three weeks straight.

684
00:34:23,810 --> 00:34:25,290
I had no choice but to come to you.

685
00:34:25,290 --> 00:34:25,929
Mr. Nie,

686
00:34:26,020 --> 00:34:27,550
let's keep personal and work separate.

687
00:34:27,550 --> 00:34:28,980
I won't pressure you about the baby,

688
00:34:28,980 --> 00:34:30,670
so don't make things hard for me at work,

689
00:34:30,670 --> 00:34:31,280
okay?

690
00:34:48,750 --> 00:34:49,949
How are you feeling?

691
00:34:52,630 --> 00:34:53,670
I'm fine.

692
00:34:54,120 --> 00:34:55,920
I just throw up everything I eat.

693
00:34:57,590 --> 00:34:58,420
I'm sorry.

694
00:34:58,710 --> 00:35:00,310
I've put you through so much.

695
00:35:02,110 --> 00:35:04,110
What's the point of saying all that?

696
00:35:04,150 --> 00:35:05,000
If you're man enough,

697
00:35:05,000 --> 00:35:07,130
then love me openly and treat me right.

698
00:35:07,670 --> 00:35:09,140
I can carry your child.

699
00:35:09,800 --> 00:35:11,550
But I can't give birth to it in a gutter,

700
00:35:11,550 --> 00:35:12,880
or in a garbage dump.

701
00:35:14,790 --> 00:35:15,620
Nie Yucheng.

702
00:35:17,070 --> 00:35:18,440
I'm a normal woman too.

703
00:35:18,710 --> 00:35:20,140
I have dreams as well.

704
00:35:20,480 --> 00:35:21,280
I want to have a child.

705
00:35:21,280 --> 00:35:22,210
I want to have a home—

706
00:35:22,210 --> 00:35:23,920
a home together with you.

707
00:35:25,360 --> 00:35:26,960
Can you picture that future?

708
00:35:37,290 --> 00:35:38,390
[Customer Signature: Nie]

709
00:35:39,680 --> 00:35:40,890
[Customer Signature: Nie Yucheng]

710
00:35:42,190 --> 00:35:43,650
Go talk to the accountant.

711
00:35:51,550 --> 00:35:52,480
What do you mean?

712
00:35:52,710 --> 00:35:54,280
You know that's not what I want.

713
00:35:54,280 --> 00:35:55,480
You're at a critical stage in your career.

714
00:35:55,480 --> 00:35:56,480
Having a baby

715
00:35:56,480 --> 00:35:57,800
would only hold you back.

716
00:35:57,800 --> 00:36:00,200
It's a burden.
Have you thought about that?

717
00:36:02,320 --> 00:36:03,720
I get what you're saying.

718
00:36:03,760 --> 00:36:05,320
You're scared I'll use the baby
to threaten you.

719
00:36:05,320 --> 00:36:06,070
I'll go get

720
00:36:06,070 --> 00:36:07,590
an abortion right now,

721
00:36:07,960 --> 00:36:09,760
and cut ties with you forever.

722
00:36:23,840 --> 00:36:24,440
Zhenzhen.

723
00:36:28,000 --> 00:36:29,110
I'm married.

724
00:36:30,960 --> 00:36:33,230
You knew it from the start.

725
00:36:33,250 --> 00:36:35,210
Then why did you get involved with me?

726
00:36:35,210 --> 00:36:36,720
Am I your pet?

727
00:36:36,800 --> 00:36:37,710
Your prey?

728
00:36:38,280 --> 00:36:40,080
Or just something to throw away?

729
00:36:40,760 --> 00:36:41,560
None of those.

730
00:36:42,440 --> 00:36:43,040
Zhenzhen.

731
00:36:44,070 --> 00:36:45,270
I honestly don't know

732
00:36:46,220 --> 00:36:47,920
how it got to this point.

733
00:36:48,230 --> 00:36:49,310
And I have no idea

734
00:36:50,470 --> 00:36:51,630
what to do now.

735
00:36:56,670 --> 00:36:58,590
Don't always think the grass is greener
on the other side.

736
00:36:58,590 --> 00:37:00,190
You think walking away from this

737
00:37:00,190 --> 00:37:01,920
will lead to something better?

738
00:37:02,100 --> 00:37:03,830
It's like waiting for a bus.

739
00:37:03,850 --> 00:37:05,510
You wait forever, and it never comes.

740
00:37:05,510 --> 00:37:07,040
So you decide to take a taxi.

741
00:37:07,440 --> 00:37:09,110
But you can't get one
and you end up back in line again.

742
00:37:09,110 --> 00:37:10,110
Then you turn around

743
00:37:10,110 --> 00:37:12,000
and the bus is already gone.

744
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:14,260
And you're right back where you started.

745
00:37:25,320 --> 00:37:28,380
Why is there suddenly
a hundred-person walking event?

746
00:37:28,800 --> 00:37:29,920
I told you to contact Director Zhang

747
00:37:29,920 --> 00:37:30,670
and sort this out!

748
00:37:30,670 --> 00:37:32,280
Did you even call him or not?

749
00:37:34,960 --> 00:37:37,960
Calling the Sports Bureau chief
is useless right now.

750
00:37:38,320 --> 00:37:40,720
Can you try the local government official?

751
00:37:40,920 --> 00:37:41,840
Enough! Cut the crap!

752
00:37:41,840 --> 00:37:43,170
Just do what I say, okay?

753
00:38:02,180 --> 00:38:03,640
Take your medicine first.

754
00:38:04,380 --> 00:38:06,710
There's millet porridge ready in the pot.

755
00:38:08,540 --> 00:38:09,800
Could you get me a bowl?

756
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:12,670
Honey.

757
00:38:23,000 --> 00:38:24,880
I asked you to talk to the official.

758
00:38:24,880 --> 00:38:26,340
Did you get through or not?

759
00:38:27,280 --> 00:38:28,280
What do you mean?

760
00:38:43,220 --> 00:38:44,220
Come lie down.

761
00:38:49,110 --> 00:38:50,570
Take your medicine first.

762
00:39:08,800 --> 00:39:09,470
Here.

763
00:39:29,840 --> 00:39:30,550
Miyu.

764
00:39:31,890 --> 00:39:33,170
I'm so tired.

765
00:39:34,370 --> 00:39:35,370
I was thinking...

766
00:39:37,280 --> 00:39:38,680
if I didn't

767
00:39:38,700 --> 00:39:40,050
have to work,

768
00:39:40,670 --> 00:39:42,600
I could stay by your side every day.

769
00:39:43,520 --> 00:39:44,770
Even doing nothing,

770
00:39:45,700 --> 00:39:47,260
just lying here next to you—

771
00:39:48,280 --> 00:39:49,940
I'd be the happiest man alive.

772
00:40:00,150 --> 00:40:00,920
Miyu.

773
00:40:01,840 --> 00:40:03,900
Just keep taking care of me like this,

774
00:40:04,920 --> 00:40:06,180
for the rest of my life,

775
00:40:07,320 --> 00:40:08,190
will you?

776
00:40:10,730 --> 00:40:11,690
Stop talking.

777
00:40:17,380 --> 00:40:18,270
I know

778
00:40:19,190 --> 00:40:20,450
you're still mad at me,

779
00:40:21,320 --> 00:40:22,110
right?

780
00:40:30,560 --> 00:40:32,460
I know a lot has happened lately.

781
00:40:33,530 --> 00:40:35,660
It has made you

782
00:40:36,070 --> 00:40:37,270
worried and anxious.

783
00:40:37,270 --> 00:40:38,230
I'm sorry.

784
00:40:39,070 --> 00:40:40,280
It's my fault.

785
00:40:40,880 --> 00:40:42,810
I didn't give you enough security.

786
00:40:43,280 --> 00:40:45,280
But I really can't live without you.

787
00:40:45,460 --> 00:40:46,120
Miyu.

788
00:40:46,760 --> 00:40:48,160
Just think of it this way—

789
00:40:48,280 --> 00:40:49,710
you're stuck with me,

790
00:40:51,800 --> 00:40:53,280
and I'll never let you go.

791
00:40:55,710 --> 00:40:56,770
What about me then?

792
00:41:00,090 --> 00:41:01,490
Where does that leave me?

793
00:41:06,320 --> 00:41:07,780
You're always in my heart.

794
00:41:08,800 --> 00:41:09,840
I, Nie Yucheng,

795
00:41:10,280 --> 00:41:11,760
have worked hard all these years

796
00:41:11,760 --> 00:41:13,070
for only one reason—

797
00:41:15,310 --> 00:41:16,100
you.

798
00:41:22,630 --> 00:41:23,800
From now on,

799
00:41:24,690 --> 00:41:26,600
I won't let you get hurt.

800
00:41:27,280 --> 00:41:28,800
I'll protect you forever,

801
00:41:30,000 --> 00:41:31,800
and protect our family forever.

802
00:41:32,550 --> 00:41:33,400
I swear.

803
00:41:34,310 --> 00:41:35,430
Will you trust me?

804
00:41:45,750 --> 00:41:47,560
♪ A flicker of dim light ♪

805
00:41:49,460 --> 00:41:51,340
♪ A bowl of warm soup ♪

806
00:41:52,830 --> 00:41:54,770
♪ People in the city ♪

807
00:41:55,540 --> 00:41:58,580
♪ Squeezing into the hustle and bustle ♪

808
00:42:00,410 --> 00:42:02,030
♪ The palms of time ♪

809
00:42:04,130 --> 00:42:07,200
♪ Grinding away the simple days ♪

810
00:42:07,890 --> 00:42:10,810
♪ Sprinkling them into this busy world ♪

811
00:42:11,850 --> 00:42:14,080
♪ To be tasted, bit by bit ♪

812
00:42:15,410 --> 00:42:18,440
♪ Embracing this radiant world ♪

813
00:42:19,120 --> 00:42:22,150
♪ Keeps the heart from fading to grey ♪

814
00:42:22,740 --> 00:42:25,860
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

815
00:42:26,600 --> 00:42:29,080
♪ Intertwined within the mundane ♪

816
00:42:28,280 --> 00:42:29,190
Some people say

817
00:42:29,400 --> 00:42:31,400
lies make life better.

818
00:42:30,730 --> 00:42:33,880
♪ Let us bravely gather up ♪

819
00:42:31,960 --> 00:42:32,800
They're like candy

820
00:42:32,800 --> 00:42:35,070
wrapped in colorful cellophane.

821
00:42:34,500 --> 00:42:37,870
♪ The forgotten past ♪

822
00:42:35,590 --> 00:42:37,800
They let you live in false sweetness,

823
00:42:37,840 --> 00:42:40,110
so you don't have to face
the bitter truth.

824
00:42:38,850 --> 00:42:41,120
♪ There may be regrets ♪

825
00:42:41,360 --> 00:42:43,760
I know I'm lying to myself.

826
00:42:42,780 --> 00:42:45,020
♪ There may be loneliness ♪

827
00:42:44,150 --> 00:42:45,800
But sometimes,

828
00:42:45,800 --> 00:42:47,480
living in a world of lies

829
00:42:46,030 --> 00:42:49,330
♪ Embracing this radiant world ♪

830
00:42:47,920 --> 00:42:50,230
is the only way to feel happy.

831
00:42:49,760 --> 00:42:52,760
♪ Keeps the heart from fading to grey ♪

832
00:42:53,690 --> 00:42:56,680
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

833
00:42:57,440 --> 00:42:59,820
♪ Intertwined within the mundane ♪

834
00:43:00,810 --> 00:43:04,130
♪ Let us bravely gather up ♪

835
00:43:04,840 --> 00:43:08,000
♪ The forgotten past ♪

836
00:43:10,350 --> 00:43:12,650
♪ Walking through this world ♪

837
00:43:13,720 --> 00:43:16,530
♪ Leaving no regrets behind ♪

